PUZZNIC:

        When playing the game, press the 'SPACE BAR' to bring up the retry
        screen, but don't release the 'SPACEBAR'.  All the time that it is
        held down the game will be paused and you can work out what to do
        without having to rush.

        Level 48: ICHI NICH
        Level 49: IGAN BARO
        Level 50: PASS WORD
        Level 51: MINA SAMA
        Level 52: NO.O KAGE
        Level 53: DE.N ANTO
        Level 54: KASH IAGA
        Level 55: RIMA SITA
        Level 56: THAN KYOU
        Level 57: MAID OOKA
        Level 58: IAGE ITAD
        Level 59: AKIM ASHI
        Level 60: TEAR IGAT

